Metcash Limited Description 




Metcash Trading Limited Australasia is a marketing and distribution company operating in the food and other fast moving consumer goods categories. It has three Business Pillars - IGA Distribution, Campbell’s Cash & Carry and Australian Liquor Marketers. IGA Distribution serves 2,500 independent retail grocery stores in Queensland, New South Wales, Victoria, South Australia and Western Australia. Australian Liquor Marketers operates 16 distribution centers across Australia and New Zealand, carrying more than 8,000 products to meet the wine, spirits and beer requirements of more than 13,000 licensed premises. Campbell’s Wholesale carries over 12,000 SKU's in confectionery, grocery, dairy, frozen, foodservice, general merchandise, liquor and tobacco products.




